               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar ”Synaxarion” for the second half of the year (fols.
                     3ra-129rb)
 I-1) Maggābit (fols. 3ra-23va)
 I-2) Miyāzyā (fols.
                     23vb-40va)
 I-3) Gǝnbot (fols. 40va-64rc)
 I-4) Sane (fols.
                     64ra-78rb)
 I-5) Ḥamle (fols. 78rc-108ra)
 I-6) Naḥāse (fols.
                     108rb-126rb)
 I-7) Ṗagʷǝmen (fols. 126rb-129rb)
 
 Additio
                     1.</summary>
